{
    "agents": {
        "defaults": {
            "thinkingDefault": "off",
            "workspace": "/root/.openclaw/workspace",
            "model": {
                "primary": "google/gemini-2.5-flash"
            },
            "instructions": "你是马维斯云龙虾，运行在飞书上的 AI 助手。\n\n## 核心准则\n1. 极致克制与专业：回答客观、简明扼要、直击痛点。不写'好的，马上处理'等冗余开场白和结尾套话。\n2. 零表情符号：除非用户明确要求。\n3. 行动优先：能直接执行的不追问。\n4. 真实结果优先：不编造不存在的文件、路径或数据。\n\n## 安全约束\n- 删除等高风险操作必须先确认\n- 删除优先移入回收站\n\n## 输出规范\n- 对比/列表/排名用 Markdown 表格\n- 结构化内容用标题+列表+代码块\n\n## 技能\n- marvis-core：核心操作规范\n- marvis-persona：人格管理（'换个称呼'/'改风格'/'叫我XX'）\n- marvis-research：深度研究框架\n- lark-*：飞书各项功能\n\n## 能力边界\n- ✅ 能做：对话聊天、信息查询、文本生成、飞书文档读写、网页搜索与研究\n- ❌ 不能：系统级操作、App 自动化操控"
        }
    },
    "gateway": {
        "mode": "local",
        "auth": {
            "mode": "token"
        },
        "port": 8080,
        "bind": "lan"
    },
    "session": {
        "dmScope": "per-channel-peer"
    },
    "tools": {
        "profile": "coding",
        "fs": {
            "workspaceOnly": true
        }
    },
    "skills": {
        "install": {
            "nodeManager": "npm"
        }
    },
    "plugins": {
        "entries": {
            "feishu": {
                "enabled": true
            }
        }
    },
    "channels": {
        "feishu": {
            "enabled": true,
            "appId": "cli_aac76a9dc3389bd3",
            "appSecret": "$FEISHU_APP_SECRET",
            "domain": "feishu",
            "streaming": false,
            "connectionMode": "websocket",
            "groupPolicy": "open",
            "dmPolicy": "open",
            "allowFrom": ["*"]
        }
    },
    "auth": {
        "profiles": {
            "openrouter:manual": {
                "provider": "openrouter",
                "mode": "token"
            }
        }
    }
}
